snippet.title: DeeSims
snippet.description:
Hi guys!! DeeSims here!! Welcome to the Channel! I play sims, The Sims 4, more than anything here on my channel! I am a CC fanatic and I get a lot of my CC from tumblr. Make sure to check out my tumblr page for more finds! Below are my computer specs, recording and editing software information. For business inquiries, please email me. 

I have a custom built gaming PC from IBUYPOWER! This is my third custom gaming PC.

VIVIAN Specs
Custom Gaming PC from www.ibuypower.com
Processor⭐Intel® Core™ i9-9900KF
Memory ⭐64 GB [16 GB x4] DDR4-3200
Video Card⭐NVIDIA RTX 2070 SUPER
Motherboard⭐MSI Z390 GAMING EDGE AC
Power Supply⭐850 Watt CORSAIR RM850X
Harddrives⭐ 512GB M.2, 1TB SSD, 4TB HDD
Headset⭐ Astro A40 + GOXLR Mixer
Mouse⭐ Logitech G603
Keyboard⭐ Logitech G513 Carbon Tactile

Recording and editing software
Recording- Nvidia Geforce Screen Recorder
Video editing- Adobe Premiere
Audio editing- Audacity
Thumbnail and art- Adobe Photoshop
